(7572, 'Lovegra 100mg tab', 'لوفيجرا 100مجم قرص', '', '9', 'Sildenafil', 'Sini pharma', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'مقوي للرجال', 'Tonic for men', '100mg', 'Sildenafil is a phosphodiesterase-5 (PDE5) inhibitor that is predominantly employed for two primary indications:
